04&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Scottish+Gaelic+Studies+journal&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Aberdeen&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.abdn.ac.uk%2Fceltic%2Fpubs.hti&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AProfessor+of+Celtic+%28Glasgow%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.gla.ac.uk/departments/celtic/ourstaff/profthomasclancy/\">\"Thomas Clancy\"</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/University_of_Glasgow\" title=\"University of Glasgow\">University of Glasgow</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">20 August</span> 2010</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Thomas+Clancy&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Glasgow&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gla.ac.uk%2Fdepartments%2Fceltic%2Fourstaff%2Fprofthomasclancy%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AProfessor+of+Celtic+%28Glasgow%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Professor_of_Celtic_(Glasgow)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.gla.ac.uk/departments/celtic/ourstaff/profthomasclancy/\">Prof Thomas Clancy staff page</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.gla.ac.uk/departments/celtic/\">University of Glasgow Department of Celtic and Gaelic</a></li></ul>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"University_of_Glasgow\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#0047AB;color: #FFD700;\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:University_of_Glasgow\" title=\"Template:University of Glasgow\"><abbr title=\"View this template\" style=\"background:#0047AB;color: #FFD700;;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:University_of_Glasgow\" title=\"Template talk:University of Glasgow\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\"background:#0047AB;color: #FFD700;;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">t</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:University_of_Glasgow&amp;action=edit\"><abbr title=\"Edit this template\" style=\"background:#0047AB;color: #FFD700;;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id=\"University_of_Glasgow\" style=\"font-size:114%;margin:0 4em\"><a href=\"/wiki/University_of_Glasgow\" title=\"University of Glasgow\"><span style=\"color:#ffd700;\">University of Glasgow</span></a></div></th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"background:#0047AB;color: #FFD700;;width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Ancient_university_governance_in_Scotland\" title=\"Ancient university governance in Scotland\"><span style=\"color:#FFD700;\">Governance</span></a></th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\" style=\"text-align:left;bord